request.description:
Server-Sent Events stream. Postman shows incoming events live in the response panel.

Event order:
- `outline` — { jobId, deckTitle, deckType, theme, canvas, canvasDims, accentColor, css, slides:[{slideNumber,title,layout,slideType,status:"pending"}] }
- `slide` (xN, out-of-order) — { slideNumber, layout, html, imageUrl, aiImage?, status:"ready" }
- `slide_error` — { slideNumber, error, status:"error" } (a single slide failed; stream continues)
- `done` — { jobId, deckId, slideCount, ms }

Copy `deckId` from the `done` event into the collection's `deckId` variable, then run Export Deck.
